content.rendered: As a leading UK wholesale distributor with a powerful reputation, we have the resources to buy and hold stock at our privately-owned 100,000 sqft warehouse. We built our market position on decisive buying decisions backed up by the scale of our resources on the ground. We built our reputation on customer service.
